 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: left; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(36, 64, 97);"><em><span style="font-size: 20px;">1.&nbsp;</span></em><span style="color: rgb(36, 64, 97); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box;">人人都可轻松上手，非常容易操作</strong></span></span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">做日课的流程——「八正习字法」十分简便，只有四个清晰标准的环节，非常容易操作。八正习字法，把练字方法和修身心法完美融合为一体，既练字，又修炼身心。</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">● 正身-正字</strong>：习字从正身开始，所谓“制之于外以安其内”，从写字这件事，训练工作生活中做事目标清晰、敬事而信的行为习惯。</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;">●&nbsp;</strong>正心-正察</strong>：掌握「深呼吸」方法，学会如何静心和调伏身心，更好面对焦虑、压力和情绪等。</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;">●&nbsp;</strong>正意-正临</strong>：「笔到意到」练习，学会观察自己的心念活动，从而训练觉察力，提高专注力。</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;">●&nbsp;</strong>正念-正校</strong>：培植正念，获得「随事专一」的能力与习惯，活在当下，提升幸福感。</span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="letter-spacing: 0px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appxUP4drJT7767/image/ueditor/87276100_1537168067.jpg" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="letter-spacing: 0px;">&nbsp;</span></p></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">“八正习字法”是一种“言下便可持循，终身以为规范”的行为习惯，这种终身受用的行为习惯的养成，只需21天！</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(36, 64, 97);"><em><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20px;">2.&nbsp;</span></em><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">人人都可运用自如，容易获得预期效果</strong></span></span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">每天10-15分钟的日课，除了标准的流程（八正习字法），只需要掌握4个简洁明了的「要诀」，便可以运用自如地做日课，进入正念，身心合一，轻松取得课程预期效果。</span>
