第12天

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appWT2TinY11178/i_5bbef01764550_vJadeOyp

<p style="text-align: center;"><br/></p><section style="line-height: 1.8; letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px 9px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(23, 54, 93); font-size: 17px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(23, 54, 93); box-sizing: border-box;">【什么是习字修身】</span></strong></span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">习字修身，是一种简便易行的身心修炼法门</strong><br/></span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">只要一笔一划地专注书写，就可以减压降负，修炼身心，同时习得一手好字，获得传统经典的滋养。</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">习字修身，是一种精进雅致的生活方式</strong></span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">每天只要10-15分钟，在充满仪式感的标准流程中，静心书写，愉悦身心。每天做「心运动」，汲取「心能量」，获得成长，遇见更好的自己！</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">习字修身具有三重功效</strong></span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">一是<strong>习字</strong>。每天的日课，在「心」上用功夫，人人可达致10倍以上的习字效果。</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">二是<strong>修身</strong>。每天的日课，犹如佛家之抄经，初习即可静心，最胜者可达禅定境界。</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">三是<strong>经典</strong>。每天的日课，用心抄写、深入研习经典，汲取经典的滋养。</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; padding: 2px 8px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(198, 2, 2); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><strong style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">成为更好的自己，改变就在当下！</strong><br/>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></section><section style="margin: -1.86em 0px 0px; padding: 2em 10px 5px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(198, 2, 2); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 20px 0%; transform: translate3d(5px, 0px, 0px); -webkit-transform: translate3d(5px, 0px, 0px); -moz-transform: translate3d(5px, 0px, 0px); -o-transform: translate3d(5px, 0px, 0px); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify; line-height: 2; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">经过长达十年的研发，最近一年四期的在线内测实验课程，今天开启公测！</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 18px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box;">席殊老师亲自主持！</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">一键报名，立即成为习字修身——这项中断百年的古代文人士大夫身心修炼的伟大传统的</span><strong style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">首批传承者、实践者！</strong>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><br/></span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">听听四期在线实验课程学员怎么说：</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; border-width: 0px 1px 1px 2px; border-style: none none none dashed; border-color: rgb(160, 160, 160); border-image: initial; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239); border-radius: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 10px 10px 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify; line-height: 1.8; padding: 0px 5px; color: rgb(44, 90, 160); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">21天的日课已近尾声，每晚的坚持，我的生活也悄然发生了一些变化，对过往的事看得越来越平淡，开车也没那么急躁了。</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: right; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">——三期学员&nbsp; &nbsp;*和平</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">通过习字修身，去除了我内心的浮躁，淡定了许多，生活中少了许多无名的烦躁和焦虑。</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: right; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">——四期学员&nbsp; &nbsp;*华玲</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">真的恋上了这10到15分钟，哪怕习字前心里如何难过，万种情绪在呼与吸之间都消散了……</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: right; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">——四期学员&nbsp; &nbsp;*方圆</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">一边体会国学的博大精深，一边享受习字带给我的安逸心境……内心安定了许多！</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: right; white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">——四期学员&nbsp; &nbsp;*扬&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0%; text-align: right; line-height: 1; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 0px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; border-bottom: 0.6em solid rgb(255, 255, 255); border-right: 0.6em solid rgb(255, 255, 255); border-top: 0.6em solid transparent !important; border-left: 0.6em solid transparent !important; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center;"><br/>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="line-height: 1; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(23, 54, 93); font-size: 17px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(23, 54, 93); box-sizing: border-box;">【课程有什么特色】</span></strong></span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: left; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(36, 64, 97);"><em><span style="font-size: 20px;">1.&nbsp;</span></em><span style="color: rgb(36, 64, 97); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box;">人人都可轻松上手，非常容易操作</strong></span></span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">做日课的流程——「八正习字法」十分简便，只有四个清晰标准的环节，非常容易操作。八正习字法，把练字方法和修身心法完美融合为一体，既练字，又修炼身心。</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">● 正身-正字</strong>：习字从正身开始，所谓“制之于外以安其内”，从写字这件事，训练工作生活中做事目标清晰、敬事而信的行为习惯。</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;">●&nbsp;</strong>正心-正察</strong>：掌握「深呼吸」方法，学会如何静心和调伏身心，更好面对焦虑、压力和情绪等。</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;">●&nbsp;</strong>正意-正临</strong>：「笔到意到」练习，学会观察自己的心念活动，从而训练觉察力，提高专注力。</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;">●&nbsp;</strong>正念-正校</strong>：培植正念，获得「随事专一」的能力与习惯，活在当下，提升幸福感。</span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="letter-spacing: 0px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appxUP4drJT7767/image/ueditor/87276100_1537168067.jpg" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="letter-spacing: 0px;">&nbsp;</span></p></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">“八正习字法”是一种“言下便可持循，终身以为规范”的行为习惯，这种终身受用的行为习惯的养成，只需21天！</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(36, 64, 97);"><em><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20px;">2.&nbsp;</span></em><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">人人都可运用自如，容易获得预期效果</strong></span></span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">每天10-15分钟的日课，除了标准的流程（八正习字法），只需要掌握4个简洁明了的「要诀」，便可以运用自如地做日课，进入正念，身心合一，轻松取得课程预期效果。</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appxUP4drJT7767/image/ueditor/7433800_1537168068.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/></p></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(36, 64, 97);"><em><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20px;">3.<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</strong></span></em><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">原汁原味的国学经典</strong></span></span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp; &nbsp; ● 通过「经典注释」学习《论语》</strong></span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 50%; padding: 0px 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-radius: 0px; border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appxUP4drJT7767/image/ueditor/26653600_1537168068.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px 3px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; padding-top: 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="border-top: 1px solid rgb(160, 160, 160); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(160, 160, 160); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: -3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 6px; height: 6px; float: left; margin-left: -1px; border-radius: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="width: 6px; height: 6px; float: right; margin-right: -1px; border-radius: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><section style="padding: 8px 10px 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="line-height: 1.4; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 13px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);">朱熹《论语集注》</span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 13px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);">古代每一个读书人必读的</span><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0px;">权威注释</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin-top: -3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 6px; height: 6px; float: left; margin-left: -3px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="width: 6px; height: 6px; float: right; margin-right: -3px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 50%; padding: 0px 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-radius: 0px; border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appxUP4drJT7767/image/ueditor/51949600_1537168068.png" style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"/>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px 3px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; padding-top: 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="border-top: 1px solid rgb(160, 160, 160); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(160, 160, 160); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: -3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 6px; height: 6px; float: left; margin-left: -1px; border-radius: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="width: 6px; height: 6px; float: right; margin-right: -1px; border-radius: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><section style="padding: 8px 10px 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="line-height: 1.4; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 13px;">钱穆《论语新解》</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 13px;">一部融会贯通、深入浅出的</span><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0px;">现代注释</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin-top: -3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 6px; height: 6px; float: left; margin-left: -3px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="width: 6px; height: 6px; float: right; margin-right: -3px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></strong></span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp; ●&nbsp;</strong>通过抄写学习国学经典</strong><br/></span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">犹如佛家抄经 —— 用最恭敬的心抄写经典，字字入心而生慧。</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appxUP4drJT7767/image/ueditor/80543400_1537168068.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="微信图片_20180917144210.jpg"/><span style="letter-spacing: 0px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="line-height: 1.5; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box;">你为什么要习字修身？</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><strong style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box;"></span></strong><br/></span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">每天的“习字修身日课”对你意味着什么？</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"></span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">冥想？瑜伽？正念？心流？</span></p><p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">练字？抄经？国学？语文？</span>&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 17px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">一项伟大传统的回归</strong></span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">从孔子到北宋二程、南宋朱熹，到明代湛若水、王阳明、到晚清曾国藩、李鸿章，一个更适合当下中国人的身心修炼方式，在中断一百年后，今天又回来了！</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">十一年前，席殊在翻阅朱熹《近思录》时，读到北宋大思想家程明道的一句话，说他习字的时候甚“敬”，非是要字好，只此是学。一下把席殊给震到了！</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">此前席殊已经阅读过大量的儒释道经典，还有过两年多的禅宗、丹道的修炼经历，就这一个被朱熹称为“圣门第一字”的“敬”字，让他豁然贯通！“敬只是随事专一、谨畏不放逸耳！”（朱熹），开启了席殊其后十年念兹在兹的问学之路，几经切磋琢磨之功，找回了这项中断百年的伟大传统！</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; border-width: 0px 2px 1px; border-style: none dashed none none; border-color: rgb(160, 160, 160); border-image: initial; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239); border-radius: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0%; text-align: left; line-height: 1; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 0px; display: inline-block; border-top: 0.6em solid rgb(255, 255, 255); border-left: 0.6em solid rgb(255, 255, 255); border-bottom: 0.6em solid transparent !important; border-right: 0.6em solid transparent !important; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px 10px 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify; line-height: 1.8; padding: 0px 5px; color: rgb(44, 90, 160); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">南宋著名的《程董学则》有“写字必楷敬”，明代大思想家湛若水制定的《大科书院堂训》中，正反各二十条，正面有“作字敬”，反面有“作字欲好”。</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">王阳明：“读明道先生书曰：‘吾作字甚敬，非是要字好，只此是学。’既非要字好，又何学也？乃知古人随时随事只在心上学，此心精明，字好亦在其中矣。”（《王阳明全集》）<span style="font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">曾国藩在给他弟弟曾国荃的书信中，劝其“在忧危忙乱中，不可废习字功夫。每日临帖一百字，收敛浮躁心气。”（《曾国藩家书》</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 0px;">席殊将这一丢失的传统称为“习字修身”，它传承了千年，它天然地和中国人有亲和性，十分适合、十分方便当下中国人修行，因为书法实在是每一个中国人血脉中流淌的文化基因。它在身心修炼方面的效果，丝毫不逊色于禅修、冥想、正念练习，因此，习字修身又称为“习字禅”、“习字冥想”、“正念习字”。</span><br/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style="text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 0px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 17px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box;">让习字修身回归中国人的日常生活</span></strong></span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 17px; box-sizing: border-box;">——习字修身，每天只要10分钟</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">席殊结合当代心理学、脑科学、教育学的成果，经过至少三轮数万学生的教学实验，实现了“习字修身日课”的流程化、标准化，简易可操作，让小学一年级的学生一节课就可以学会。</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">“习字修身日课”也适用于当下碎片化的场景，每一个忙碌的中国人都可以“随时随地做日课”。在《21天论语日课》前四期的实验课程中，就有很多同修分享他们在火车上、飞机上，在约会的等侯中做“日课”的体验，迅速地进入正念，收获心流。</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">一支笔、一张《日课纸》，再配上导师引导语音频，习字修身就是这么简单，但其成效深不可测！获得心流，进入正念、禅定，以致明心见性也不好说，但至少可以让自己平静下来，让自己更加专注、从容，自然而然习得一手好字，获得传统经典的滋养。</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;<img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appxUP4drJT7767/image/ueditor/94776000_1537168068.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="微信图片_20180917134702.jpg"/></span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="text-align: left; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 17px;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;">总有一门课程、一张《日课纸》适合你当下</span></strong></span><strong style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 17px; box-sizing: border-box;">的需求</span></strong></span><span style="text-align: left; letter-spacing: 0px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 17px; box-sizing: border-box;">——习字修身课程体系</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">为满足不同人群的不同的习字修身需求，席殊建立了习字修身课程体系。</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">《21天论语日课》</strong>是习字修身的入门课程，课程包括三堂视频课（什么是习字修身、怎样做日课和《论语·学而篇》通解）；21张《日课纸》、8张活页习字帖及开学、结业作业；21天的日课引导音频；21天的日课书写示范视频；以及导师讲解书法技法、解读《论语集注》的视频等。</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 20px 0%; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 95%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(158, 158, 158) 0px 0px 4px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -7px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; width: 90%; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appxUP4drJT7767/image/ueditor/18058000_1537168069.jpg" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"/><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(120, 144, 156); font-size: 13px;">21天论语日课·日课纸</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(120, 144, 156);">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(120, 144, 156);"><br/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style="text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">每天的10-15分钟的日课，只需打开「</span><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(54, 96, 146);">做日课</span></strong></span><span style="text-indent: 0em; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">」音频，在舒缓的背景音乐和导师深沉的导引中，迅速进入正念，完成当天的《日课纸》。非常的宁静、平和，身心合一，在抄写经典的过程中习得一手好字。</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">《21天唐诗日课》</strong>则是适合孩子的习字修身入门课，家长可以和孩子一起亲子共修。</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">与部编语文教材同步的<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">《语文同步日课》</strong>也已发售！内容包括了《语文》课本中《写字表》的全部生字、《词语表》的全部词语，以及所有背诵篇目、段落，还有语文园地中的“日积月累”。</span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="letter-spacing: 0px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 20px 0%; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 95%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(158, 158, 158) 0px 0px 4px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -7px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; width: 90%; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appxUP4drJT7767/image/ueditor/46889400_1537168069.png" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 12px 0% 8px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: left; color: rgb(120, 144, 156); padding: 0px 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 13px;">语文同步日课·一年级上·日课纸</span><br/>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">每天15分钟，跟随</span><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(54, 96, 146);">日课导引音频</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">，完成当天的《日课纸》，一个学期下来，孩子不可能写不好字，语文成绩一定会有明显的提升，孩子会变得更加沉静、从容，专注力明显提升，并养成受益终身的良好的行为习惯。</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(54, 96, 146);"><strong><span style="font-size: 15px;">我们只会比古人更加浮躁、更加焦虑、更加不安，借用曾国藩的话说，对于今天的中国人，在忧危忙乱中，不可不习字修身，每天只要10分钟，收敛浮躁心气！再借用王阳明的话说，字好亦在其中！</span></strong></span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(54, 96, 146);"><strong><span style="font-size: 15px;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appxUP4drJT7767/image/ueditor/1588500_1537169664.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="微信图片_20180917153343.jpg"/></span></strong></span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(23, 54, 93); font-size: 17px;"><strong style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">【订阅课程，你将得到什么】</strong></span><br/>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">● 3次视频直播课</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); text-indent: 32px;">● 8个专题视频</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); text-indent: 32px;">●&nbsp;</span>21天日课音频</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); text-indent: 32px;">●&nbsp;</span>21天的书法技法图解</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); text-indent: 32px;">●&nbsp;</span>21天经典及注释图文</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); text-indent: 32px;">●&nbsp;</span>21天日课书写示范视频</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); text-indent: 32px;">●&nbsp;</span>21张电子版《日课纸》</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); text-indent: 32px;">●&nbsp;</span>8张活页习字帖、开学结业作业</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 20px 0%; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 95%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(158, 158, 158) 0px 0px 4px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0% -7px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; width: 90%; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appxUP4drJT7767/image/ueditor/68237500_1537168070.jpg" style="vertical-align: middle; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"/><span style="font-size: 13px; color: rgb(120, 144, 156); letter-spacing: 0px;">活页习字贴·描红</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(120, 144, 156); letter-spacing: 0px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(23, 54, 93); font-size: 17px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">【21天课程结束后，你将获得什么】</strong></span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">习字方面</span></strong>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); text-indent: 32px;">●&nbsp;</span>获得正确的习字理念</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); text-indent: 32px;">●&nbsp;</span>掌握高效的习字方法</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); text-indent: 32px;">●&nbsp;</span>初步习得一手规范的硬笔行书</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">修身方面</span></strong>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); text-indent: 32px;">●&nbsp;</span>掌握一套身心修炼的基本方法</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); text-indent: 32px;">●&nbsp;</span>提高自我觉察力、专注力，养成「八正」行为习惯</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); text-indent: 32px;">●&nbsp;</span>学会克服压力、焦虑、抑郁等负面心理</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); text-indent: 32px;">●&nbsp;</span>身心和谐，回归平和宁静、澄明觉知的生命状态</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); text-indent: 32px;">●&nbsp;</span>更有智慧地面对生命中的挑战与困境</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); text-indent: 32px;">●&nbsp;</span>身修而后家齐，使家庭和谐、美满、幸福</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">经典方面</span></strong>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); text-indent: 32px;">●&nbsp;</span>获得对《论语·学而篇》的初步悟解，汲取经典的滋养</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); text-indent: 32px;">●&nbsp;</span>了解中国心性义理之学，及其存养修身之道</span>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appxUP4drJT7767/image/ueditor/88857800_1537168070.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="微信图片_20180917143742.jpg"/>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><strong style="color: rgb(23, 54, 93); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;">【课程适合哪些人】</span></strong><br/>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="color: rgb(59, 59, 59); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px;">适合关注内心、渴望自我成长的成年人，以及初高中学生，书法零基础人群。</span>
